value.0: The wooden surface on this round table has been worn and scratched from overuse. There are even initials etched into the woodwork along with other self-glorifying inscriptions.
The tabletop of this magnificently built round table has finely inlaid patterns using several types of wood, making it a prized furnishing for anyone with an eye for decor.
